data.description: Location, location, location. Calling all Contractors and Investors!  2-Family home situated in the heart of Brookfield, minutes from the common, Rt. 9, & Lake Lashaway. Both units consist of 2 bedrooms, a full bath, kitchen & a sun filled living room. Exterior features include good sized lot & paved driveway for off street parking. This multifamily is a diamond in the rough, needs some TLC to bring it back to its original charm. Here is your chance to build some instant sweat equity! See it today!
